members.name: REVERB
members.comment: Represents a control over a set of possible reverberation settings. Each reverberation setting is described by an instance of the ReverbType class. (To access these settings, invoke EnumControl.getValues() on an enumerated control of type REVERB.)
Constructs a new enumerated control type.

param: name - the name of the new enumerated control type

name: javax.sound.sampled.EnumControl$Type
comment: An instance of the EnumControl.Type inner class identifies one kind of enumerated control. Static instances are provided for the common types.
